timeline.title: BTC spikes to 24k, after 0.25% raise
timeline.content: The market reacts positive after the expected raise, and Powell talking about disinflation.

timeline.title: Genesis files for bankruptcy
timeline.content: Genesis, a part of DCG filed for bankruptcy. People fear that Grayscale, also a part of DCG and holder of est. 600'000 BTC, also might have problems.

timeline.title: Inflation falls to 6.5%
timeline.content: Bitcoin pumped to 18k due to positive news from the FED. Get squeezed, shorts!

timeline.title: Taiyo pilots launched staking
timeline.content: Taiyo pilots launched staking platform! Every faction can earn their own currency.

timeline.title: BONK abandoning DeGods
timeline.content: 500 billion $BONK was burnt, which was initially meant to be airdropped to DeGods holders.

timeline.title: Solana rises from the ashes.
timeline.content: After BONK and Vitalik tweeting optimistic about solana, price rises to 13$.

timeline.title: Welcome in 2023!
timeline.content: The year starts good with $BONK an airdrop to the solana community.

timeline.title: SBF expected plead not guilty.
timeline.content: SBF is likely to plead not guilty to eight counts of fraud at a hearing next week, according to a source close to the matter.

timeline.title: Taiyo pilots minted out!
timeline.content: The third main collection of the taiyo ecosystem has minted out.

timeline.title: Solana falls below 10$
timeline.content: Solana dropped below 10 dollars for the first time since 2021.

timeline.title: DeGods is moving to Ethereum
timeline.content:
Dust Labs decided to leave solana.
DeGods is migrating to Ethereum & Yoots is moving to Polygon.

timeline.title: Solana drops to 14$
timeline.content: With the fall of FTX, the biggest supporter of solana is gone, and solana is dipping and dipping.

timeline.title: Google cloud becomes a solana validator
timeline.content: Google cloud announced they will host solana validators.
